snippet.title: Meghan Markle Slammed For Having 'Zero Class' By Former Model
snippet.description:
It's the interview that launched a thousand tabloid headlines: Prince Harry and his wife Meghan Markle, sitting down with Oprah Winfrey to spill gallons of tea about the royal family. The Duke and Duchess of Sussex claimed, among other juicy details, that one of the royals was "concerned" about baby Archie's skin color, and that Meghan wasn't properly educated on royal family etiquette. Needless to say, there have been some emotional responses to the tell-all, including from some fellow celebs, such as Piers Morgan and Bethenny Frankel. Recently, Meghan Markle was slammed for having "zero class" by a former model. Here's why.
